[b]Allowing a specific amount of connections per IP[/b]
(Thanks to Yz86Racer)

[quote="snpteen"]Is it possible to make it so it allows 2 connections per IP instead of just 1?[/quote]

[quote="Yz85Racer"][code]if(!connections.contains(connectingHost)) {[/code]

Replace that with:
[code]if(connectionsFromIP(connectionHost) < 3) {[/code]

Add this method:
[code]private int connectionsFromIP(String host) {
	int occurences = 0;
	for(Object i : connections.toArray()) {
		if(i.toString().equals(host)) {
			occurences++;
		}
	}
	return occurences;
}[/code][/quote]


